{"tid":1255923,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"BTS遭澳洲主持 嘲係同志涉歧視","createTime":"2019-06-24T17:15:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T12:37:27.000Z","uid":136738,"like":91,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"956ef0f46f9c92b9746a4e2d82dab7baa3b06d21","tid":1255923,"uid":136738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T17:15:11.000Z","msg":"2019/06/21 (週五) 12:00上午 都市日報<br />\n<br />\n韓團防彈少年團（BTS）人氣席捲全球，惟前晚卻淪為澳洲電視台Channel9節目《20 to One》的取笑對象！節目中男主持聲稱從未聽過BTS，笑指如果北朝鮮領導人金正恩鍾意男偶像，南北韓就不會開戰，但補充：「不過見到呢個組合，我就覺得話題性遠不及炸彈爆炸。」其後有嘉賓又嘲BTS打入美國排行榜冠軍，但得一位成員識講英文，並譏諷成員是同志，結果激嬲一眾粉絲，電視台即向觀眾致歉，但堅稱只為增加趣味性，沒違反播放守則。"},{"pid":"33bd84e1b717a536d33dd52e42e9ac6ad3072630","tid":1255923,"uid":204370,"like":108,"dislike":18,"score":90,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T17:16:39.000Z","msg":"人地都係講事實啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d96a476b03a15a81173ae9d8adfa6d34ccc6dd12","tid":1255923,"uid":143093,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T17:16:41.000Z","msg":"諗起會員對唔住大佬(現黑)"},{"pid":"201b2399271c0904a033b57c06ef8a8a169bc40b","tid":1255923,"uid":1790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T17:27:13.000Z","msg":"同志組織出黎未？"},{"pid":"87be7fb3a1f8a312c728067867a9e4c89b0bc15f","tid":1255923,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T17:29:31.000Z","msg":"Where is 邊邊???"},{"pid":"f73ce61a55bb87ad771b2c15b5486face88c719b","tid":1255923,"uid":251836,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T17:31:54.000Z","msg":"事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b854914a512101a97065e5d2e071871d6e490dd","tid":1255923,"uid":215715,"like":21,"dislike":11,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T17:35:03.000Z","msg":"班崇韓撚真係成班恐怖份子咁撚樣 kpop塔利班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbe675023702958494d7ccad5defc03d1c908266","tid":1255923,"uid":152432,"like":3,"dislike